quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,123,Babu A’di boosi bayingasia Abarumwa
  26,124,(Betsulisie) Olwa Omusiani wabu Hud yababoolela mbu; “koo shimulamuria tawe?’’
  26,125,Toto esie endi khwinywe Omurumwa Omwisikwa
  26,126,Kho murie Nyasaye ne muwulile
  26,127,"Ne shebasaba khukano omurungo tawe, Omurungo kwanje kulisa khu Nyasaye Omulesi webiloonje biosi"
  26,128,"“Koo, mumbakhanga buli khwitulo, eshitsulisio shiokhukhola kalia kabulamwo oluchendo"
  26,129,Ne mumbakhanga tsing’oba mpara mbu mulimenya tsinyanga tsiosi
  26,130,Ne nimusera museranga nobufuru
  26,131,Kho murie Nyasaye ne muwulile
  26,132,Ne Murie ulia owabahelesia kalia akamumanyile
  26,133,Yabahelesia emiruko nende Abana abasiani
  26,134,Nende “emikunda nende tsisebele”
  26,135,Toto ebaririranga eshinyasio shieyinyanga ikhongo
  26,136,"nibaboola mbu; “ni halala butswa awo, khwifwe nokhuchelela nohomba noobula okhuchelela.”"
  26,137,Kano shikalisa halali ebima biabandu bakhale
  26,138,Ne efwe shikhulihebwa eshinyasio tawe
  26,139,"Mana nibamuyingasia, nenikhubasishia, toto mukano khulimwo nende ameeko, halali abanji mubo shibali Abasuubili tawe"
  26,140,Ne toto Nyasaye wuwo niye Owamani Owetsimbabaasi muno